  "title": "(Urgent) General Worker -Wiring Technician| Cleaner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Multiple Locations Available</p></li><li><p>On-the-job training provided</p></li><li><p>Basic + OT = High Gross</p></li></ul><h2><strong></strong></h2><h2><strong>Technician </strong>- <strong>Job Description</strong></h2><p>Responsible for supporting daily operations and basic technical tasks to ensure the workplace runs smoothly, safely, and efficiently.</p><h2><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h2><p><p><ul><li>Install and connect electrical wiring according to drawings</li><li>Test and check wiring for safety and proper function</li><li>Troubleshoot basic wiring faults and report issues</li><li>Follow safety rules and keep work area tidy</li></ul></p></p><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Able to perform general operational and basic technical tasks</p></li><li><p>Able to follow safety guidelines and work instructions</p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p><h2><strong>Cleaner – Job Description</strong></h2><p>You will be responsible for maintaining cleanliness, hygiene, and a safe environment.</p><h2><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Clean and sanitize resident rooms, bathrooms, and common areas</p></li><li><p>Sweep, mop, and vacuum floors</p></li><li><p>Collect and dispose of waste properly</p></li><li><p>Refill cleaning supplies and toiletries when needed</p></li><li><p>Follow cleaning schedules and hygiene standards</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Able to follow cleaning instructions and schedules</p></li></ul><p><br /><br />To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Yuphine Lee | R22108749</strong></p>",
